      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-[var(--ink)] leading-tight">What Are Measurables in Business? How to Track What Matters for Effective Performance Management</h1>
      <p class="text-[var(--ink-mute)] mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">Measurables, including key performance indicators (KPIs), let organizations track progress, assess strategy, and make informed decisions. This guide covers what measurables are, which ones matter for EOS teams, and how AI agents enable real-time tracking on the OTP platform.</p>
